Title: Sansheng's Golden Fish Scales
---
Sansheng asked Xuefeng, " the golden fish scales
that pass through the net are not investigated, what is used for
food?"

Feng said, "Wait until you come out of the net, then

Sheng said, "A Learned and Virtuous One of fifteen
hundred people and still don't know the 'head of the word'
(huatou). "

Feng said, " an old monk in residence managing
numerous affairs."
